sentences.sentence: Nonfat dry milk is an inexpensive proteinaceous eluent.
sentences.translation: 脱脂奶粉是廉价的蛋白质洗脱剂。

sentences.sentence: The effect of the eluent concentration on retention value was studied.
sentences.translation: 研究了淋洗液浓度对保留值的影响，当淋洗液浓度增大时，保留值减小。

sentences.sentence: Objective to study the influence of eluent of different polarity on triptolide content.
sentences.translation: 目的研究不同极性洗脱液对雷公藤内酯醇含量的影响。
